        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add 3 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until golden and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
