      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1706632457451-x200.jpg",
