        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
