      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>Vietnamese-style caramelised & braised basa </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and <strong>carrot salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
